summary: Replacement textures for the default High Elf eyes.
descriptionHtml:
This mod replaces the default High Elf eyes, adding blue eyes, glowing orange eyes, and evil red eyes. 

[color={red}][ Installation - Extract the rar content into your Syrim main directory ][/color]

[color={red}][ Uninstalling - Remove  \"eyehighelf.dds\" , \"eyehighelfdarkyellow.dds\" and \"eyehighelforange.dds\" from Data/textures/actor/character/eyes ] [/color]
author: vp007
